model.name: Mitrophanov2013 - Simulation of Hockin Blood Coagulation Model under reduced temperature

body.p: Blood coagulation model using an updated Hockin2002 model. New reactions for factor X and V activation by IXa and mIIa respectively (reactions R28 and R29, parameters k43 and k44). Changes to parameters k32 and k38 (appendix not found for cited reference [Danforth 2009] so parameters from Mitrophanov2011 were used). Model introduces formula for adjusting kinetic rates for reduced temperatures.
